             were indicted, for <rs id="t18300415-352-off1904" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18300415-352-off1904" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18300415-352-off1904" type="offenceSubcategory" value="simpleLarceny"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18300415-352-cd1905" type="crimeDate">1st of April</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18300415-352-off1904 t18300415-352-cd1905"></join>, 7 handkerchiefs, value 12s.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t18300415-352-victim2921" type="victimName">
                     Thomas 
                     Bech
                  <interp inst="t18300415-352-victim2921" type="surname" value="Bech"></interp>
